Step 1: click on file, click on OpenPGP key pair
Step 2: enter name and enter email address and also click on  protect the generated key with a passphrase 
Step 3: enter the passphrase or password and press enter
Step 4: goto to notepad type some text
Step 5: click on sign/encrypt notepad and enter passphrase
Step 6: click on decrypt/verify notepad
